<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Her iconic curves made her a household name. </p>

<p>And Kelly Brook complemented her hourglass physique with a chic floral dress as she strutted through London towards Global Radio studios on Tuesday.</p>

<p>The radio host, 40, embraced autumnal style as she headed to work to present her Heart FM show.  </p>

<p>Floral number: Kelly Brook complemented her hourglass physique with a chic floral dress as she strutted through London towards Global Radio studios on Tuesday</p>

<p>She was spotted wearing a black smock dress peppered with pink and cream flowers. </p>

